---
layout: layouts/main.njk
title: Global Brain Consortium - Home
eleventyNavigation:
    key: home
    title: Home
    order: 1
---

{% row %}
    <div class="bg-c-fg1-l grid place-content-center max-w-screen-xl mx-auto lg:py-12 lg:grid-cols-12 overflow-hidden video-container h-full">
        <div class="bg-white-transparent absolute w-full h-full z-10">
        </div>    
        <div class="place-self-center lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-6 mx-8 my-8 px-8 z-20 py-8 overflow-hidden bg-white/80">
            <h1
                class="text-center uppercase text-colour-dark  lg:text-left mb-4 text-3xl/snug font-extrabold tracking-normal md:text-4xl/snug xl:text-5xl/snug ">
                Global Brain Consortium</h1>
            <p
                class=" text-center lg:text-left mb-5 mt-5 font-light text-colour-dark mx-15 md:mx-5 md:ml-0 md:mr-6 lg:mb-8 md:text-lg/normal lg:text-xl/normal  ">
                A diverse network of brain researchers, clinicians, and institutions committed to achieving improved and more equitable health outcomes worldwide.
            </p>
            <div class="flex mx-auto justify-center md:justify-start">
            <a href="{{'/about/' | url}}" class=" mx-auto lg:mx-0 md:mt-5 button-square-primary new-button ">
                    Our Mission
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5"
                        stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 -mr-1">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
     
        <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="{{'/assets/images/content/gbc-bg-big-crop.png' | url}}">
        </div>
    </div>
{% endrow %}


{% row %}
    <div class="bg-c-fg2-l   grid place-content-center max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 mx-auto lg:py-16 lg:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="px-10 py-2 max-w-sm md:max-w-md lg:mt-0 lg:col-span-4 place-self-center mx-auto ">
            <img src="{{'/assets/images/content/gbc-bg.png' | url}}">
        </div>
        <div class="mr-auto px-2 place-self-center lg:col-span-8">
            <p
                class="select-none text-center lg:text-left mb-5 mt-5 font-light text-white mx-15 md:mx-5 md:ml-10 lg:mb-8 md:text-lg/normal lg:text-xl/normal  ">
                The Global Brain Consortium builds collaborative and dynamic relationships among globally-oriented health researchers.
            </p>
            <p
                class="select-none text-center lg:text-left mb-5 mt-5 font-light text-white mx-15 md:mx-5 md:ml-10 lg:mb-8 md:text-lg/normal lg:text-xl/normal  ">
                Our mission is to address the challenges that need to be overcome to drive multinational collaborative efforts in support of Global Precision Brain Health by strengthening linkages between neuroscientists across borders and disciplines.
            </p>
            <div class="flex mx-auto justify-center md:justify-start mx-15 md:mx-5 md:ml-10">
                <a href="{{'/resources/0/' | url}}" class=" mx-auto lg:mx-0 md:mt-5 button-square-primary  ">
                    News & Events
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5"
                        stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 -mr-1">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
{% endrow %}

{% row %}
    <div class="bg-c-fg1-l max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-5 mx-auto lg:px-16 lg:py-8">
    <div class="bg-c-bg2-l   max-w-screen-xl rounded-xl px-8 pb-8 pt-8 mx-auto my-8 solid-shadow  ">
      
      <h3
        class="text-center text-gray-500  lg:text-left mb-4 text-sm/snug tracking-normal md:text-md/snug xl:text-lg/snug ">
        Feb 26, 2025</h3>
      <h3
      class="text-center text-colour-dark lg:text-left mb-4 width-full text-2xl/snug font-extrabold tracking-normal md:text-3xl/snug xl:text-4xl/snug ">
      An article featuring Pedro Valdes-Sosa published in Science</h3>
      

      <div class="flex flex-wrap max-w-screen-xl py-8 mx-auto">
        <div class="px-10 py-2 max-w-sm lg:w-1/3 justify-center mx-auto"> 
            <img src="{{'/assets/images/content/front-page/pedro_valdes-sosa-2.jpg' | url}}">
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto place-self-center {% if resource.data.image != ''%}md:w-2/3{%else%}md:w-full{%endif%}">
          <p
            class="select-none text-center lg:text-left mb-5 mt-5 font-light text-colour-dark lg:mb-8 md:text-lg/normal lg:text-xl/normal  ">
             Cuban neuroinformaticist Pedro Antonio Valdés Sosa wrote in October 2023 to Xi Jinping, China’s leader, hailing the two Communist nations’ budding collaboration in brain science.
          </p>
          <div class="flex mx-auto justify-center md:justify-start mx-15">
                <a href="https://www.science.org/content/article/cuban-brain-researcher-went-viral-chinese-tv-here-s-why" class=" mx-auto lg:mx-0 md:mt-5 button-square-primary  ">
                    Read More
                    <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                        d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
{% endrow %}

